<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="help-page">
  <div class="help-hero">
    <h1>Help Center</h1>
    <p>Everything you need in one place</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Tabs -->
  <div class="help-tabs">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('shipping')">Shipping Policy</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('return')">Return & Exchange</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('faqs')">FAQs</button>
  </div>

<!-- Shipping -->
<div class="tab-content active" id="shipping">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Shipping Policy</h2>

    <h3>Delivery Time</h3>
    <p>
      Orders are delivered within 5–7 business days in Cairo, Giza, and Alexandria,
      and up to 8 business days for other governorates.
    </p>

    <h3>Delivery Attempts</h3>
    <p>
      Our shipping partner will attempt delivery up to 3 times and will contact you
      using the phone number provided during checkout.
    </p>

    <h3>Undelivered Orders</h3>
    <p>
      If the order cannot be delivered after 3 attempts, it will be automatically
      returned and marked as a returned order.
    </p>

    <h3>Important Note</h3>
    <p>
      Please make sure your contact details and delivery address are accurate
      to avoid delays or missed deliveries.
    </p>

    <h3>Need Help?</h3>
    <p>
      For any questions or support, feel free to contact us via email:
      <strong>veekegy@gmail.com</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Return -->
<div class="tab-content" id="return">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Veek Return & Exchange Policy</h2>

    <p>
      At Veek, we want you to love every piece you order. If you are not completely
      satisfied, you can return or exchange your order within 14 days of delivery.
    </p>

    <h3>Conditions for Return / Exchange</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Items must be unworn, unwashed, and in original condition.</li>
      <li>Customized or printed items are non-returnable unless defective.</li>
      <li>Sale, clearance, or end-of-season items are non-refundable.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Defective or Wrong Items</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        If your item is defective or the wrong product was delivered, Veek covers
        all shipping costs.
      </li>
      <li>
        A replacement or refund will be provided at no extra charge.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Shipping & Costs</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Customers are responsible for return shipping unless the item is defective
        or incorrect.
      </li>
      <li>
        Exchange shipping costs are collected by the courier upon delivery.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How to Return or Exchange</h3>
    <p>
      Customers can request returns or exchanges through:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: <strong>veekegy@gmail.com</strong></li>
      <li>Instagram</li>
      <li>WhatsApp</li>
      <li>Facebook</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Our team will confirm your request and guide you through the process.
    </p>

    <h3>Refunds & Exchanges</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Refunds are processed through the original payment method within
        10–14 business days after receiving the returned item.
      </li>
      <li>
        Exchanges are processed within 5–10 business days depending on stock availability.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Customer Rights & Legal Notice</h3>
    <p>
      This policy is in accordance with the Egyptian Consumer Protection Law
      No. 181 of 2018.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you have any questions, our team is always here to help and make your
      experience smooth and fair.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQs -->
<div class="tab-content" id="faqs">
  <div class="faq-box">

    <details>
      <summary>How can I purchase your products?</summary>
      <p>You can purchase through our website.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Can I open the package before paying the courier?</summary>
      <p>
        Unfortunately, no. Couriers are not allowed to wait for try-ons
        or return with opened packages.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Where can I find the size chart?</summary>
      <p>
        The size chart is available in the product gallery on each product page.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>How long does delivery take?</summary>
      <p>
        Orders are delivered within 5–7 business days in Cairo, Giza,
        and Alexandria, and up to 8 business days for other governorates.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Can I make my order arrive faster?</summary>
      <p>
        Unfortunately, delivery times cannot be expedited.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Do you have a physical store?</summary>
      <p>No, we operate exclusively online.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Do you allow exchanges / returns?</summary>
      <p>
        Yes, according to our return and exchange policy.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>How can I request refund, exchange, or cancel order?</summary>
      <p>
        Contact us at <strong>veekegy@gmail.com</strong> or via social media pages.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>How can I contact you?</summary>
      <p>
        Through DM, Contact Us page, or email:
        <strong>veekegy@gmail.com</strong>
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>What happens if courier cannot deliver my order?</summary>
      <p>
        After 3 attempts, the order will be returned automatically.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Can I order two sizes of the same item?</summary>
      <p>
        No, such orders are not allowed and may be canceled automatically.
      </p>
    </details>

  </div>
</div>
</section>

<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
  background:#f8f8f8;
}

/* HERO */
.help-hero{
  text-align:center;
  padding:40px 20px 20px;
}

.help-hero h1{
  font-size:38px;
  margin:0;
}

.help-hero p{
  color:#666;
  margin-top:10px;
}

/* TABS */
.help-tabs{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:12px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  padding:20px;
}

.tab-btn{
  border:none;
  background:#fff;
  padding:12px 20px;
  border-radius:30px;
  cursor:pointer;
  font-weight:600;
  transition:.3s;
  box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.tab-btn.active,
.tab-btn:hover{
  background:#111;
  color:#fff;
}

/* CONTENT */
.tab-content{
  display:none;
  max-width:900px;
  margin:auto;
  padding:10px 20px 50px;
}

.tab-content.active{
  display:block;
}

.card{
  background:#fff;
  padding:25px;
  border-radius:18px;
  box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
}

.card h2{
  margin-top:0;
}

/* FAQ */
.faq-box details{
  background:#fff;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  padding:16px;
  border-radius:14px;
  box-shadow:0 5px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
}

.faq-box summary{
  cursor:pointer;
  font-weight:600;
}

.faq-box p{
  margin-top:12px;
  color:#555;
}

/* MOBILE */
@media(max-width:768px){

  .help-hero h1{
    font-size:28px;
  }

  .help-tabs{
    overflow-x:auto;
    flex-wrap:nowrap;
    justify-content:flex-start;
    padding:15px;
  }

  .tab-btn{
    min-width:max-content;
    font-size:14px;
    padding:10px 16px;
  }

  .card{
    padding:18px;
  }
}
</style>

<script>
function showTab(tabId){
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(tab=>{
    tab.classList.remove('active');
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(btn=>{
    btn.classList.remove('active');
  });

  document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');
  event.target.classList.add('active');
}
</script>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
